# 🚗 Obstacle Avoiding Car (Tinkercad Simulation)

An Arduino-based **Obstacle Avoiding Car** simulation built using Tinkercad that detects obstacles using an ultrasonic sensor and automatically changes direction to avoid collisions.

---

