## 📍 Project Overview

This project simulates a **self-driving obstacle avoiding robot car** using Arduino in Tinkercad.

The system uses an ultrasonic sensor to detect obstacles in front of the vehicle and automatically controls motor direction to avoid collisions.

⚠️ This is a **simulation-based project** (no physical hardware used).

---

